678
00:35:35,490 --> 00:35:37,320
are negligible.

679
00:35:37,320 --> 00:35:38,400
There are no dividends.

680
00:35:38,400 --> 00:35:41,640
Gold does not pay out dividends.

681
00:35:41,640 --> 00:35:44,040
There are no real
benefits either,

682
00:35:44,040 --> 00:35:45,765
