712
00:37:13,860 --> 00:37:15,160
Let me do another example.

713
00:37:15,160 --> 00:37:16,140
So this is gold.

714
00:37:16,140 --> 00:37:18,370
What about gasoline?

715
00:37:18,370 --> 00:37:20,850
Gasoline it turns out, is
